text: "Just being in the finals, one, is way more than I ever expected and the fact that I've got support from so many great people, and that they look up to me and watch this show and support me, just ... I don't even have the words, just a lot of thanks," Ross said.
title: Cubs' David Ross finally hits it out of the park on 'Dancing with the Stars'
